    "actions": [
      {
        "startDie": 1,
        "endDie": 2,
        "name": "Corrosive Touch (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Fleshmelt Slime extends a pseudopod towards a target, attempting to touch and dissolve their flesh. It makes a melee attack, dealing D6 Acid damage on a hit.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 3,
        "endDie": 4,
        "name": "Putrid Eruption",
        "description": "<div><p>The Fleshmelt Slime violently erupts, releasing a burst of noxious fumes and corrosive fluids around it. Creatures caught in the area must succeed on an Endurance check or take 2D4 Acid damage and have their weapon Skills reduced by -5 until the end of combat.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 5,
        "endDie": 6,
        "name": "Devour Essence (Magical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Fleshmelt Slime extends a tendril towards a creature, attempting to drain their life force. The target must succeed on an Endurance check or take 2D4 Necrotic damage and have their Toughness maximum reduced by the same amount until they finish a rest. The Fleshmelt Slime regains Health equal to the damage dealt.</p></div>"
      }
    ],
    "description": "<div><p>This abominable ooze is a repulsive amalgamation of melted and rotten flesh, its form constantly shifting and quivering. Its surface appears as a ghastly palette of decomposing bodies, their tortured features forever frozen in twisted agony. As it oozes and stretches, it leaves a trail of putrid ichor and dissolving bone in its wake, leaving the very ground it touches barren and tainted. The Fleshmelt Slime feeds on the life essence of its victims, its acidic touch melting flesh and reducing bones to a grotesque pulp.</p></div>",
